data.value: This program allows a user to send torque readings from a compatible AWS Torque Product to an open spreadsheet. Simply start the program, select a port, click 'Activate Spreadsheet Transfer', click on a cell in your spreadsheet, and start sending data from the tester. If you find a bug, please send details to Taylor@Awitness.com. For more information about our company, please visit Awitness.com
